metadata.name: HIGH TIDE (Music Video) #1/100
metadata.created_by: Cam Murdoch, June Jissle, and Tommy Trill
metadata.description:
Filmed Sunday October 16th 2022 at Ocean View Fishing Pier in Norfolk, VA by Tommy Trill.

The song "HIGH TIDE" was produced by June Jissle and is performed by Cam Murdoch.

Collectors of the Sound.xyz edition of this song will automatically receive a free claim for the music video, with a public open edition taking place afterwards.

Holding a token from the HIGH TIDE smart contract unlocks access to the HIGH TIDE podcast, future air drops, and the Surf Noir universe.
